snippet.title: Roadside Assitance Simulator - Trailer HD
snippet.description:
Experience the everyday duties of a roadside assistance team in this realistic mix of simulation and management game.
 
Direct your rescue team from your roadside assistance center. Unlock new regions and try to attract as many new customers as possible through successful and efficient operations. You can also roll up your own sleeves and repair broken down cars in the street. One by one, you’ll unlock new buildings, vehicles, rescue helicopters and technologies. Are you ready to make the roads safer in traffic-heavy urban areas and during the harsh winter 
months?
Let’s find out!
